---
// CAPCS Core Ingredient — 方案C：满宽深海断言带 + 下方要点/数据（背景仍为浅色）
---

<section id="science" class="section science">

  <!-- ── 满宽深海断言带（深色图承担戏剧感，section 底仍为浅色）── -->
  <figure class="science-hero reveal">
    <img
      class="science-hero-img"
      src="/assets/science-deepsea.webp"
      alt="纯净海域——贻贝钙肽CAPCS®的深海起源"
      loading="lazy"
      width="1600"
      height="900"
    />
    <div class="science-hero-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <figcaption class="science-hero-content">
      <p class="science-hero-eyebrow">专研贻贝钙肽 CAPCS<sup>®</sup></p>
      <h2 class="science-hero-title">30 秒快速止痒<br />效果媲美弱效激素</h2>
      <p class="science-hero-sub">天然无激素。提取自纯净海域的珍稀贻贝，以纯物理回流反渗技术萃取，无任何化学溶剂残留。</p>
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class="section-inner science-body">

    <div class="science-points reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">30 秒快速止痒</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">临床验证止痒速度优于弱效激素（氢化可的松），效果等同于弱效激素。切断“搔抓恶性循环”，从根源缓解皮肤问题。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">13 年自主研发</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">由生物学博士后团队研发，纯物理回流反渗技术萃取。发表于《中华皮肤科杂志》与 SCI 期刊，机理与临床双重验证。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="science-point">
        <span class="science-point-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="science-point-text">
          <h3 class="science-point-title">五维金标准安全</h3>
          <p class="science-point-body">无激素、无抗生素、无防腐剂。经口无毒、入眼无刺激、人体斑贴无刺激、多次皮肤刺激无刺激、4000+ 争议成分不添加。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="science-data reveal reveal-rise">
      <div class="science-data-row">
        <div class="science-data-item">
          <span class="science-data-value">79%</span>
          <span class="science-data-label">止痒有效率</span>
        </div>
        <div class="science-data-item">
          <span class="science-data-value">67%</span>
          <span class="science-data-label">特应性皮炎治疗有效率</span>
        </div>
        <div class="science-data-item">
          <span class="science-data-value">6×</span>
          <span class="science-data-label">提高激素有效率</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="science-data-note">数据来源：《中华皮肤科杂志》与 SCI 期刊临床研究 · 全国 1000+ 公立医院皮肤科临床验证</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .science {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding-top: var(--space-4xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-6xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── 满宽深海断言带 ── */
  .science-hero {
    position: relative;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5xl);
    min-height: clamp(440px, 64vh, 660px);
    display: flex;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .science-hero-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .science-hero-scrim {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.78) 0%,
      oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.55) 42%,
      oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.12) 78%
    );
  }

  .science-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    align-self: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--content-padding);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .science-hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: oklch(90% 0.06 200);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .science-hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .science-hero-sub {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: oklch(96% 0.01 200 / 0.85);
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  /* ── 要点列表（编辑式，居中限宽）── */
  .science-points {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .science-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .science-point + .science-point {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .science-point-num {
    flex: none;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    font-size: 0;
    background: url('/assets/list-marker.png') center / contain no-repeat;
    margin-top: 0.2em;
  }

  .science-point-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .science-point-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-soft);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* ── 临床数据（编辑式，无盒无竖线）── */
  .science-data {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: var(--space-2xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
  }

  .science-data-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: clamp(var(--space-2xl), 8vw, var(--space-6xl));
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .science-data-item {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 20ch;
  }

  .science-data-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 200;
    color: var(--color-brand-dark);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .science-data-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .science-data-note {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .science-hero {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
      min-height: clamp(380px, 56vh, 520px);
    }
    .science-hero-scrim {
      background: linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.35) 0%,
        oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.55) 60%,
        oklch(14% 0.05 245 / 0.72) 100%
      );
    }
    .science-hero-content {
      align-self: flex-end;
    }
    .science-points {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }
    .science-point {
      gap: var(--space-md);
      padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    }
    .science-point-num {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
    }
    .science-data-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
